with.prompt:
Set up a repository for a SvelteKit application.

Repository owner: ${ .input.owner // "giteaadmin" }
Repository name: ${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }
Description: ${ .input.description // "A polished SvelteKit demo built by Claude Code" }

1. Check if the repo exists:
   curl -sf 'http://gitea-http.gitea.svc.cluster.local:3000/api/v1/repos/${ .input.owner // "giteaadmin" }/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }' -H 'Authorization: token '"${GITEA_TOKEN}"''
   If 404, create it:
   curl -X POST 'http://gitea-http.gitea.svc.cluster.local:3000/api/v1/user/repos' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -H 'Authorization: token '"${GITEA_TOKEN}"'' -d '{"name": "${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }", "description": "${ .input.description // "A polished SvelteKit demo built by Claude Code" }", "private": false, "auto_init": true}'

2. Clone the repo (fresh):
   rm -rf /tmp/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }
   git clone http://giteaadmin:${GITEA_TOKEN}@gitea-http.gitea.svc.cluster.local:3000/${ .input.owner // "giteaadmin" }/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }.git /tmp/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }

3. Configure git:
   cd /tmp/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" } && git config user.email 'claude@agent.local' && git config user.name 'Claude Code Agent'
4. If the repo is empty (no commits), create an initial commit:
   echo '# ${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }' > README.md && git add README.md && git commit -m 'Initial commit' && git push origin main

IMPORTANT: Always cd to /tmp/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" } first.

Report the workflow completion.

1. cd /tmp/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }
2. Show the latest commits: git log --oneline -5
3. Show the repo URL: echo 'Repo: https://gitea-ryzen.tail286401.ts.net/${ .input.owner // "giteaadmin" }/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" }'
4. Summarize what was built for this brief: ${ .input.ui_brief // "A polished one-page SvelteKit demo designed to look strong in a captured walkthrough." }

IMPORTANT: Always cd to /tmp/${ .input.repo // "launch-day-dashboard-demo" } first.
